{"content": "I need to multiply 531 \u00d7 816 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n531\u2089 = 5\u00d79\u00b2 + 3\u00d79\u00b9 + 1\u00d79\u2070 = 5\u00d781 + 3\u00d79 + 1\u00d71 = 405 + 27 + 1 = 433\u2081\u2080\n\n816\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 1\u00d79\u00b9 + 6\u00d79\u2070 = 8\u00d781 + 1\u00d79 + 6\u00d71 = 648 + 9 + 6 = 663\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n433 \u00d7 663 = 433 \u00d7 (600 + 63)\n= 433 \u00d7 600 + 433 \u00d7 63\n= 259,800 + 27,279\n= 287,079\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n287079 \u00f7 9 = 31897 r 6\n31897 \u00f7 9 = 3544 r 1\n3544 \u00f7 9 = 393 r 7\n393 \u00f7 9 = 43 r 6\n43 \u00f7 9 = 4 r 7\n4 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 4\n\nReading from bottom to top: 476716\u2089\n\n**Step 4: Verification**\n\n476716\u2089 = 4\u00d759049 + 7\u00d76561 + 6\u00d7729 + 7\u00d781 + 1\u00d79 + 6\u00d71\n= 236196 + 45927 + 4374 + 567 + 9 + 6\n= 287079\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n476716", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1245, "completion_tokens": 458}